data.description: Welcome to 70 Crossroads Cove in Ward, Arkansas! This charming property offers a serene and quiet atmosphere just outside of town. Situated on over 1 acre of land, this home features an open and split floor plan. Spacious kitchen with cabinet and counter space for all your culinary needs. .The primary bathroom is designed with your comfort and convenience in mind. It boasts a thoughtful layout that includes both a bathtub and a separate shower. The backyard offers a great space to entertain as well as peaceful moments in the outdoors. HVAC 2017, Roof 2022 Schedule your showing today!
